9.2.11 Phase Boundaries
Phase 1 excludes:
• Probability scoring
• Numeric likelihood percentages
• Machine learning confidence weighting
• Cross-user outcome modeling
Phase 2+ may introduce:
Structured interpretive strength metadata
Statistical annotation
Jurisdictional variation mapping
But must not convert into predictive payout scoring.

9.2.12 Final Design Doctrine
Confidence is:
Structural clarity
Not prediction
Not advice
Not outcome modeling
It exists to:
Reduce ambiguity
Reduce hallucination
Increase auditability
Improve AI indexability
Preserve trust
